# --- Boost Real Programming Languages ---

# Ignore docs, markdown, and non-code files
*.md linguist-documentation
*.txt linguist-documentation
*.pdf linguist-documentation
*.json linguist-generated
*.yml linguist-generated
*.yaml linguist-generated

# Ignore images and static files
*.svg linguist-generated
*.png linguist-generated
*.jpg linguist-generated
*.jpeg linguist-generated
*.gif linguist-generated
*.ico linguist-generated

# Ignore entire folders commonly not code
/docs/* linguist-documentation
/public/* linguist-documentation
/assets/* linguist-documentation
/static/* linguist-documentation

# Optional: Ignore frontend HTML/CSS if you want backend-focused profile
# *.html linguist-documentation
# *.css linguist-documentation
